ber"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>matlab运行的收敛过程如下所示，A硬币正面朝上的概率由最初猜测的0.6收敛为了最终的0.80，B硬币正面朝上的概率由最初猜测的0.5收敛到了最终的0.52。</p>
